reviews.text: It is beyond imagination that we have two servings of sizzling steaks at special price for the afternoon session in the amount of HK$130. The taste of the steak is good that commensurates with its price and is served with soup, garlic toasts and soft drinks. You will have the ambience of a high class restaurant if you avoid going there during busy hours. Worth trying once or twice and if steaks do not please your palates, there are plenty of otheratat choices at even lower prices. Just great to spend an hour there in a lazy afternoon.
